304 6966, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1737 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25566,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/06\/darkness-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32851,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Oppression: Injustice will be darkness on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, oppression will be darkness on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2447, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2579 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22769,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/27\/reckoning-fully-account\/","url_meta":{"origin":32851,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hisab: Whoever is interrogated will be punished","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is fully taken to account on the Day of Resurrection will be punished.\u201d I said, \u201cHas not Allah Almighty said: He will soon have an easy reckoning?\u201d (84:8) The Prophet said, \u201cThat is not the reckoning,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/least-punished-in-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":32851,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jahannam: The least punished man in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most lightly punished of the people of Hellfire on the Day of Resurrection is a man under whose feet are placed two hot coals by which his brain boils.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6561,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28991,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/allah-expose-riya-shirk-asghar\/","url_meta":{"origin":32851,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: Allah will expose hypocrites on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever acts to be heard, Allah will make him heard. Whoever acts